io.spine.tools.mc.js.code.text

Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.tools.mc.js.code.text.Parser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.spine.tools.code.Element, Snippet

    public final class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
implements Snippet
    The code of a generated parser for a Protobuf message.

    This parser should be generated for all messages except standard ones like Any, int32, Timestamp. The parsers for these standard types are manually created and require no code generation.

    Code provided by the class is in ES5 standard since Protobuf compiler generates JavaScript in ES5.

      • parseMethodCall

        public static java.lang.String parseMethodCall(java.lang.String parserVariable,
                                               java.lang.String valueToParse)
        Obtains the string representing a call to a method parsing an object into a message.

        The method can be used to reference the a call to a handcrafted parser as well as for a generated parser.

        Parameters:
        parserVariable - the name of the parser variable
        valueToParse - the object to parse
